*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Module PBO_6001 OUTPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE pbo_6001 OUTPUT.
* SET PF-STATUS 'xxxxxxxx'.
* SET TITLEBAR 'xxx'.
  PERFORM change_screen_state.
ENDMODULE.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form change_screen_state
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM change_screen_state .
  CASE sy-tcode.
    WHEN 'VF03'.
      LOOP AT SCREEN.
        screen-input = '0'.
        MODIFY SCREEN.
      ENDLOOP.
    WHEN OTHERS.
  ENDCASE.
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Module STATUS_0001 OUTPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE status_0001 OUTPUT.
* SET PF-STATUS 'xxxxxxxx'.
* SET TITLEBAR 'xxx'.
  CASE sy-tcode.
  WHEN 'VF03'.
    LOOP AT SCREEN.
      SCREEN-INPUT = '0'.
      MODIFY SCREEN.
    ENDLOOP.
  WHEN OTHERS.
  ENDCASE.
ENDMODULE.
